Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:02:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick! Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Song of Willow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A voice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stopping, Nico Robin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, you woman\Nwhose very life is a crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lucci! Drag her along!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab her by her hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... you still think that the\NStraw Hats are coming to your rescue?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously still laying your\Nhopes on such weak-looking pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only feeling you'll have is a sense of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll endlessly atone for your\Nsin of having lived until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nico Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What was that?! I just heard a voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The space has opened up. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Pigeon guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Resounding Bad News! Buster Call Invoked!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed... I'll say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you've come\Nthis far... all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could come this far by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I wouldn't even wanna come by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you guys, I'm not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon all my friends will come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really starting to get the hang of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to feel kinda sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sailor. Don't say\Npathetic things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not a sailor. I'm a hero who\Nhails from the island of snipers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although my best friend\NUsopp-kun is a sailor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They dodged!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't do things that are uncalled for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?! What's that supposed\Nto mean?! How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good... It's so\Nslippery that I can't stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what a creepy power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a bunch of sour grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you don't come close to me\Nwhen it comes to strength and beauty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I gave you the gift of silky skin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you can at least come\Na bit closer to my beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very sweet of you. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a limit to how far you\Ncan go, right?! There's a limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a limit to women's desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,500)}"Ticked!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you do it to yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I don't need it, because\NI'm already beautiful enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait. I'm about to get you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow... That damn deer-gorilla!\NHow dare he mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, the key! The key!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better hurry to that secretary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deer-gorilla! Wait, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather those who can still fight to\Nthe front of the Courthouse! Do it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flinch! Capture the traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call us traitors?! Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, the Navy, who's been\Nbetraying us for the past 50 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're pirates to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with pirates\Nfighting against the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Oimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll change our strategy and\Nbring them down individually!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack unit! Concentrate\Nyour fire on Kashii's feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We bow to nobody in human\Nwave attacks! Keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Kashii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oimo is next! Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The situation outside has changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The giants who changed sides\Nhave been trying hard for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess they are at the end of their rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that a pirate would get this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone, come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CP9! What the hell are you all doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate has gotten this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're holding is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A... A golden transponder snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:06.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Navy"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The silver transponder snail\Nhas received a signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.22,0:12:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been\Nrequested by Admiral Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have five of the Vice Admirals\Nnear the destination respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's quicker to head\Nthere from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How quick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible to get there within 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immediately have ten battleships\Nget ready to set sail,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and summon five Vice Admirals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be swift!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The destination is Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have ten battleships get\Nready to set sail immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Oh, crap! This one is\Nthe portable transponder snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done? I wasn't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things, I pressed the button\Non the golden transponder snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I requested a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I requested a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Buster Call? D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Some internal communication?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish! Cancel it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Robin's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or it'll be a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? "Cancel it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey. Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:13:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.41,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call is great, isn't it?\NWhat's wrong with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Chief Spandam's voice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.01,0:14:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the chief of Cipher Pol No. 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to hand you over\Nto the Government smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I requested a Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see no problem in that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.02,0:14:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to annihilate\Nthe pirates for sure in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?!\NThat won't be the end of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no humanity in that attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Chief... but who's the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attack will completely burn\NEnies Lobby to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buildings, people... the very island itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nightmarish concentrated fire that\Nsacrifices everything to achieve its goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what happened in\NOhara twenty years ago. That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. It means that this is\Nvery important to the Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that idiot Cutty Flam has\Nburned the blueprints for Pluton...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your existence is the only\Nclue to the ancient weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A military power that can turn this\Nwhole era upside down is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it improves our chances of killing\Nthose idiots trying to get you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if it causes the death\Nof thousands of soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can say that it's an unavoidable\Nsacrifice for our glorious future!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all things, my promotion is at stake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's he saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna sacrifice us?! You gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of people's lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that CP9 is the\NGovernment's secret organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we need 100 deaths in\Norder to save 1,000 lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.42,0:17:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll kill those 100 without\Nhesitation on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mercilessness is also\Na necessity for true justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, those incompetent soldiers\Nwho couldn't stop the invading pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are better off dead, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That portable transponder snail...\NThe line is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone hear what I just said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So... my name is Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Leave the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been\Nrequested on Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay on the island, you won't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:18:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--B...\N--Buster Call...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like Buster Call has been requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.06,0:18:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that man doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like there's some sort of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me who's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your hope is gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're used to situations like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate kid, what kind of\Ndestiny were you born with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting even more interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Buster Call has been requested!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battleships are coming? Why are\Nthe Navy soldiers running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman said that the island\Nwill be burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the Government's island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! If you guys're running away,\Nat least untie us first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Buster Call!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be dead if we stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring some ships to the front!\NGet ready to sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy is coming to attack this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're we gonna do?!\NIsn't this dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been dangerous ever since\Nwe set foot in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Bro?! What's gonna\Nhappen to Big Bro Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.94,0:19:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If he doesn't come back here,\Nwe can't go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:20:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will... happen to all of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to waste time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we have to take them out quickly\Nand hurry to the Gates of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.69,0:20:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to get the handcuffs off?\NOr a way to escape from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the renowned sword, Nose Storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to give me a nice name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you open your mouth\Nand say such stupid stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the pirates really get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how are you going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...take responsibility for it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was Robin speaking from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other side of these doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you pass. At least\Ngive me time to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way.\NRobin's behind those doors, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's there. So what?\NYou won't be able to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'll go there to see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! My entire body is slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Now that Buster Call has\Nbeen requested, playtime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A-A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirage Tempo. I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Five Namis? Nami Strikes Back with Mirages!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
